- Plugin name:
greek: Téleios (Τέλειος) = english: complete
pronunciation: pronounced like TELL-e-os
.


- File Naming Notes:
Cmd = Command
Lst = Listener
.


- Interesting classes and methods:
LivingEntity
    addPotionEffect(PotionEffect effect)
Player
    setInvisible(boolean b)
ItemStack
    serialize()
ItemMeta
.


- Chat message / command feedback colors:
green (§a) 	/ gold (§6): success message
yellow (§e) / gold (§6): info message
red (§c) 	/ gold (§6): fail message
.


- Conventions:
mark current problem with // FIXME: ...
avoid exceptions using if statements
Sample statements can be found in SampleCode
don't use Double.NEGATIVE_INFINITY as it is a messenger value in GlobalFunctions
.


- Data structure for the plugin.yml:
commands:
   commandName1:
      aliases: [ alias1, alias2 ]
      permission: teleios.segmentName1.commandName1
      description: description1
      usage: /commandName1, /commandName1 (keyWord1|keyWord2) <placeholder1>

permissions:
   teleios.segmentName1.commandName1:
      description: Allows use of the commandName1 command.
      default: true
   teleios.segmentName1.commandName2Read:
      description: Allows querying the argumentName argument using /commandName2.
      default: true
   teleios.segmentName1.commandName2:
      description: Allows use of the commandName2 command.
      default: op
.


